name: Financial Freedom
description: Financial freedom is earned, not given. Financial Freedom is a Solana-born community for people who know they were meant for more than working, worrying, and hoping it all works out. We share ideas, accountability, and conviction so more of us can buy back our time. Financial Freedom ($FF) is a community-driven project launched via Bonk.fun. The token trades on a USD1 pair and should be considered a high-risk digital asset.
